{"type":"message","id":"40bf38b5","parentId":"cef9e324","timestamp":"2026-05-02T01:59:34.270Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"So I can see that 23 videos were transcribed - 7 from April 27 and 16 from April 28 (wait, let me count more carefully):\n\nApril 27 folder has 7 files:\n1. ChatGPT 5.5 Codex\n2. Claude Code Desktop Deep Dive\n3. Claude Code Secrets + Linear Clone\n4. OpenClaw + Hermes Combo\n5. OpenClaw Full Tutorial\n6. OpenClaw Memory System\n7. The Best Claude Design Workflow\n\nApril 28 folder has 24 files (but one is master-summary.md, so 23 video files):\n1. 100 hours of OpenClaw lessons in 35 minutes\n2. 5 OpenClaw use cases that will actually improve your life\n3. 5 OpenClaw use cases that will make you a productivity MACHINE\n4. 5 insane ClawdBot uses cases you need to do immediately\n5. 6 OpenClaw use cases I promise will change your life\n6. Anthropic just blocked OpenClaw. \n7. Claude Code Mobile just changed AI coding forever (Remote Control)\n8. Claude Opus 4.6 is a MASSIVE upgrade for ClawdBot and Claude Code (full guide)\n9. Claude Opus 4.6 — Greatest model for OpenClaw ever\n10. DO NOT use a VPS for OpenClaw (major warning)\n11. Did Hermes Agent just kill OpenClaw (full guide)\n12. How to build an army of OpenClaw agents\n13. How to make ClawdBot 10x better (5 easy steps)\n14. How to run ClawdBot for DIRT CHEAP\n15. I just spent $20,000 on OpenClaw. \n16. MASSIVE CLAUDE CODE LEAK! THIS CHANGES EVERYTHING!\n17. OpenClaw is 100x better with this tool (Mission Control)\n18. OpenClaw is the most powerful AI tool I've ever used in my life. Here's how to set it up\n19. The only OpenClaw tutorial you'll ever need (March 2026 edition)\n20. This is the CHEAPEST and EASIEST way to set up ClawdBot\n21. Why you NEED to be running local AI models (FULL beginners guide)\n22. You NEED a Mac Mini for ClawdBot\n23. You NEED to do this with OpenClaw immediately!\n24. You're Using OpenClaw Wrong If You Don't Use Discord\n25. master-summary.md (this is a summary file, not a video)\n\nSo that's 24 transcribed videos total. The master-summary.md file is just a consolidated overview, not a separate video transcription.\n","thinkingSignature":"26afab865905106edcd9c423792ecd4f29c7286b7eb75dd51472178e0a9fb7e7"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\nYes Bobby! I remember — you had me transcribe **23 Alex Finn videos** from his YouTube channel (@AlexFinnOfficial). They're all saved in:\n\n**`~/Desktop/Research/SecondBrain/Research/alex-finn/`**\n\nHere's the breakdown:\n\n**April 27 batch (7 videos):**\n- ChatGPT 5.5 Codex\n- Claude Code Desktop Deep Dive\n- Claude Code Secrets + Linear Clone\n- OpenClaw + Hermes Combo\n- OpenClaw Full Tutorial\n- OpenClaw Memory System\n- The Best Claude Design Workflow\n\n**April 28 batch (16 videos):**\n- 100 hours of OpenClaw lessons in 35 minutes\n- 5 OpenClaw use cases that will actually improve your life\n- 5 OpenClaw use cases that will make you a productivity MACHINE\n- 5 insane ClawdBot uses cases you need to do immediately\n- 6 OpenClaw use cases I promise will change your life\n- Anthropic just blocked OpenClaw. Here's what you need to do immediately\n- Claude Code Mobile just changed AI coding forever\n- Claude Opus 4.6 is a MASSIVE upgrade for ClawdBot and Claude Code\n- DO NOT use a VPS for OpenClaw (major warning)\n- Did Hermes Agent just kill OpenClaw\n- How to build an army of OpenClaw agents\n- How to make ClawdBot 10x better\n- How to run ClawdBot for DIRT CHEAP\n- I just spent $20,000 on OpenClaw. Here's why...\n- MASSIVE CLAUDE CODE LEAK!\n- OpenClaw is 100x better with this tool (Mission Control)\n- OpenClaw is the most powerful AI tool I've ever used\n- The only OpenClaw tutorial you'll ever need (March 2026 edition)\n- This is the CHEAPEST and EASIEST way to set up ClawdBot\n- Why you NEED to be running local AI models\n- You NEED a Mac Mini for ClawdBot\n- You NEED to do this with OpenClaw immediately!\n- You're Using OpenClaw Wrong If You Don't Use Discord\n\nThere's also a `master-summary.md` file that likely has an overview of all the videos.\n\nWas there something specific you wanted me to do with them — look something up, update them, or add more?"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":1767,"output":1056,"cacheRead":39168,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":41991,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777687158823,"responseId":"06448d76924cb45aa6288ae7b10bf3ae"}}
