{"type":"message","id":"4f83b8fe","parentId":"d35163f6","timestamp":"2026-05-02T02:26:51.519Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Bobby wants to redo all the Alex Finn transcriptions from scratch. This is a big task - 23 videos. I need to figure out a good approach.\n\nFirst, I need to understand what we need:\n1. The correct video list in chronological order (oldest to newest)\n2. Transcribe each one\n3. Summarize each one\n\nFor getting the correct order, I should:\n1. Go to Alex Finn's YouTube channel\n2. Get ALL his videos with their upload dates\n3. Sort them oldest to newest\n4. Identify which ones we transcribed before and which was the stopping point\n\nThe stopping point video (Qkqe-uRhQJE) was supposed to be the last one. Let me search for that video on his channel to confirm.\n\nLet me start by:\n1. Going to Alex Finn's channel to get the full video list with dates\n2. Cross-reference with what we have\n3. Build the correct chronological list\n4. Then transcribe from oldest to newest\n\nI should use the browser tool to go to the channel and get the video list. This will be the most reliable way to get accurate ordering.\n\nLet me plan this out with Bobby before diving in.\n","thinkingSignature":"1131bfe1ac11295b1b479c7205b785a9b256979762fff190e4436ff053d11618"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\nHere's what I'd suggest — a methodical approach:\n\n**Step 1: Get the correct video list**\nI go to Alex Finn's YouTube channel (@AlexFinnOfficial), pull ALL his videos with upload dates, and get the **full chronological list** oldest to newest. This way we know exactly what we're working with.\n\n**Step 2: Confirm the stopping point**\nVerify which video Qkqe-uRhQJE actually is — so we know where to stop.\n\n**Step 3: Transcribe & summarize in order**\nGo oldest → newest, one at a time (like we did before). Each video gets its own file with full transcript + summary.\n\n**Step 4: Save to the same folder structure**\n- `~/Desktop/Research/SecondBrain/Research/alex-finn/2026-04-XX/` \n- One .md file per video\n\n**The question is: do you want me to pull a completely fresh video list from YouTube right now?** That way we start with accurate, up-to-date info rather than relying on memory of what we did before.\n\nWant me to start now?"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":53100,"output":475,"cacheRead":192,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":53767,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777688794848,"responseId":"064493db7c2de893ca3bcdfa174f7741"}}
