{"type":"message","id":"242b7541","parentId":"43994955","timestamp":"2026-05-02T02:44:37.759Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Oh I see - Bobby just wants me to go from the most recent videos (which we already have in the \"Latest\" tab) down to the stopping point video Qkqe-uRhQJE. I don't need to scroll through all 247. I already have the \"Latest\" tab showing the most recent videos. I just need to go from newest down to the stopping point.\n\nLet me start with the most recent video and work backward until I hit Qkqe-uRhQJE. I'll use the \"Latest\" tab I already have, then work backwards through the list until I find and complete that stopping point video.\n\nLet me start transcribing the most recent video and keep going backwards until I hit the stopping point.\n","thinkingSignature":"b80a75580ad1b02f095f1a4f5ddd09267195bb672bc075b27a4aee3d23c67bec"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\nGot it — starting now! I'll go from most recent backwards to the stopping point. First up:\n\n**Video 1** (most recent): `ChatGPT 5.5 Codex is the greatest AI coding tool ever. Here's how to use it` — `https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=iz3_xhi6iQE`\n\nTranscribing now..."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":83233,"output":223,"cacheRead":192,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":83648,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777689857915,"responseId":"06449802220d33e2578dc57826157321"}}
