{"type":"message","id":"ed9a2dd5","parentId":"bbe550d7","timestamp":"2026-05-02T03:17:54.301Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Bobby is asking if video 3 is still working and if everything will be done by tomorrow. Let me check on the status. I'm currently transcribing video 3. Let me be honest with Bobby - these are long videos (some 30+ minutes) and there could be many of them. At 23 videos (number from before), plus potentially new ones, this could take quite a while. Let me be transparent about the timeline.\n\nI should be honest - at roughly 5-10 minutes per video (transcription + writing file), 23+ videos could take hours. If we're going by tomorrow morning, that might be ambitious unless we're very fast. Let me be real with Bobby about the timeline.\n","thinkingSignature":"591ccbdb285e8827c99f32aa3a826d9561629789018812bfc6b77036de069a66"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\nHonestly Bobby — I'm going to be real with you. These videos are LONG (some 30+ minutes each), and there could be 20+ videos total. At roughly 5-10 minutes per video for transcription + writing the file, this could take **many hours**.\n\nIf you're planning to wake up and have it all done, that's probably not realistic unless you want me working through the night (which I can do — I don't sleep! 😄).\n\n**Question for you:** Do you want me to:\n1. **Work through the night** — get as many done as possible, report to you every few videos\n2. **Take breaks** — do, say, 5 videos, then check in with you, then continue\n3. **Do a smaller batch tonight** — just the most recent few and pick up more later\n\nLet me know and I'll adjust accordingly. I don't want to burn through everything too fast if you want to stay involved in the process."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":88994,"output":346,"cacheRead":320,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":89660,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total