{"type":"message","id":"fa5e4856","parentId":"4930624b","timestamp":"2026-05-02T03:20:33.983Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Bobby wants me to do all of them in order and doesn't care how long it takes. I should just continue working through them and update him periodically. I should now complete video 3 and keep going.\n","thinkingSignature":"3cf2dd0fae2b92f3f6fc1a409293cdea7876ffdf51ed75e9ee9f32f50c2649b4"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n**Video 3 complete!** Moving to video 4!\n\n---\n\n**Video 3:** `ChatGPT 5.5 Codex: I can't believe they did this...`\n**URL:** https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cgp-gfSbmNE\n**Runtime:** 30m 36s\n\n**What it's about:**\nAlex digs into some surprising, almost unbelievable things about ChatGPT 5.5 Codex that most people don't know. He covers:\n\n- **Hidden capabilities** that Codex has that most users never discover — things buried in settings and workflows\n- **Codeex vs other tools** — surprising advantages Codex has that nobody is talking about\n- **Speed and efficiency** breakthroughs — how it's so much faster than Claude Code for certain tasks\n- **Multi-modal features** most people miss — image gen, file handling, real-time browser control all integrated\n- **Real-world productivity wins** — specific examples of tasks that used to take hours now taking minutes\n- **The \"can't believe they did this\" moments** — features that shouldn't work as well as they do\n\nHe spends time comparing it directly to Claude Code and showing where Codex wins decisively, especially for people on a budget.\n\n---\n\nNow transcribing **Video 4:** `The best Claude Design workflow you'll ever see…` — `https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_v_heNg0j1c`"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":84741,"output":327,"cacheRead":4864,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":89932,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp