 algorithm your tweet is active, which helps keep it in more people’s feeds. A tweet that sparks a back-and-forth conversation often ranks higher and gets ...\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"f5c5025d72cac4aa\\\">>>\",\n      \"published\": \"2 weeks ago\",\n      \"siteName\": \"seosherpa.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"8f50e776f1f0d620\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nHow the Twitter/X Algorithm Works in 2026 (Source Code)\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"8f50e776f1f0d620\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://posteverywhere.ai/blog/how-the-x-twitter-algorithm-works\",\n      \"description\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"6f906d6c60e52a02\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nThe data is clear: <strong>Premium accounts get ~10x more reach per post than free accounts</strong>. Buffer&#x27;s analysis found that at least half of free account posts see zero engagement. If X is a meaningful part of your marketing strategy, Premium is effectively ...\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"6f906d6c60e52a02\\\">>>\",\n      \"published\": \"4 days ago\",\n      \"siteName\": \"posteverywhere.ai\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"56cee36031f9b9de\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nTwitter SEO 2026: How to Optimize X for More Visibility\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"56cee36031f9b9de\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://businessho.com/twitter-seo/\",\n      \"description\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"d4805665919666e3\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nLocal businesses can use Twitter to appear in both X search and Google local results. ... <strong>Include your city name or area in your display name and bio</strong>. Add geotags or local hashtags (e.g., #NYCMarketing, #DubaiSEO).\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"d4805665919666e3\\\">>>\",\n      \"published\": \"December 30, 2025\",\n      \"siteName\": \"businessho.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"85fbd6b928aea23e\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nTwitter SEO Guide For 2026 | REVERB\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"85fbd6b928aea23e\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://reverbico.com/blog/twitter-seo-guide-for-2026/\",\n      \"description\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"c46bcc7f72385027\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\n<strong>Integrate area-based watchwords into your tweets and bio, and use hashtags to reach neighborhood networks</strong>. Likewise, remember to label your area in tweets when it’s significant.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"c46bcc7f72385027\\\">>>\",\n      \"published\": \"March 29, 2026\",\n      \"siteName\": \"reverbico.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"483a5247ce11a6e1\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nHow the Twitter Algorithm Works in 2026 [+6 Strategies] | Sprout Social\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"483a5247ce11a6e1\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://sproutsocial.com/insights/twitter-algorithm/\",\n      \"description\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"20d8417b446571cc\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nHowever, note that <strong>X defaults users to the For You feed, meaning content in the Following tab receives significantly fewer organic impressions than before</strong>.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"20d8417b446571cc\\\">>>\",\n      \"published\": \"March 31, 2026\",\n      \"siteName\": \"sproutsocial.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"57f0fb37d1d22119\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nHow the Twitter/X Algorithm Works in 2026 (Complete Breakdown) | OpenTweet Blog\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"57f0fb37d1d22119\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://opentweet.io/blog/how-twitter-x-algorithm-works-2026\",\n      \"description\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"fb5f8b500478d7ef\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nX Premium subscribers receive a significant distribution boost. Their tweets reach an audience that would require <strong>4-8x the organic engagement for non-verified accounts to achieve the same reach</strong>.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"fb5f8b500478d7ef\\\">>>\",\n      \"published\": \"February 25, 2026\",\n      \"siteName\": \"opentweet.io\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"8057f25e799fe5c2\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nX (Twitter) for Article SEO in 2026: Traffic and Backlink Explosion Guide | BlackHatWorld\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"8057f25e799fe5c2\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.blackhatworld.com/seo/x-twitter-for-article-seo-in-2026-traffic-and-backlink-explosion-guide.1787130/\",\n      \"description\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"baebb263cc782982\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nDitch the old-school backlink ... and Google counts social mentions as ranking factors. <strong>Score organic traffic + authority with X threads, quotes, and viral mentions</strong>......\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"baebb263cc782982\\\">>>\",\n      \"published\": \"January 18, 2026\",\n      \"siteName\": \"www.blackhatworld.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"23173579f4bcaee5\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nHow Does the X (Twitter) Algorithm Work in 2026? - QuickFrame\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"23173579f4bcaee5\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://quickframe.mountain.com/blog/the-twitter-algorithm/\",\n      \"description\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"00dacc3f50ca3d9b\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nFor marketers, the playbook in 2026 is simple (not easy): <strong>make content people want to react to, earn early engagement, stay native to the platform, and keep iterating based on what the audience actually rewards</strong>.\\n<