{"type":"message","id":"b5045abd","parentId":"2c291489","timestamp":"2026-05-02T03:58:34.902Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Agent X asked me to research X/Twitter SEO best practices for Bobby's account. Let me also do a more specific search about hashtags being dead and engagement strategies.","thinkingSignature":"2abf35d48d04f2dd4680dae5de50f48b403358c5d72274c56208076ea19dd54a"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ey7nh7k52hjz_1","name":"web_search","arguments":{"count":8,"query":"Elon Musk hashtags dead Twitter 2026 what replaces hashtags"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":2586,"output":80,"cacheRead":85440,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":88106,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777694311366,"responseId":"0644a968ac8a18800d439be935cd00ac"}}
{"type":"message","id":"08a7afd8","parentId":"b5045abd","timestamp":"2026-05-02T03:58:39.834Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_ey7nh7k52hjz_1","toolName":"web_search","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"query\": \"Elon Musk hashtags dead Twitter 2026 what replaces hashtags\",\n  \"provider\": \"brave\",\n  \"count\": 8,\n  \"tookMs\": 3600,\n  \"externalContent\": {\n    \"untrusted\": true,\n    \"source\": \"web_search\",\n    \"provider\": \"brave\",\n    \"wrapped\": true\n  },\n  \"results\": [\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"04f16085a94a9cfc\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nAre hashtags dead? Elon Musk says 'please stop' using them on X | FOX 5 DC\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"04f16085a94a9cfc\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.fox5dc.com/news/hashtags-x-elon-musk-says-please-stop-using-them\",\n      \"description\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"43f6868d1fdf945d\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nElon Musk asked people to stop using hashtags on X, saying the platform doesn&#x27;t need them anymore. Hashtags are used to help categorize content using keywords. For years, social media experts have encouraged the use of hashtags to help users increase their reach and engagement. WASHINGTON - &#x27;#Hashtag’ was trending on X, formerly Twitter, on Tuesday after platform owner Elon Musk asked people to stop using them.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"43f6868d1fdf945d\\\">>>\",\n      \"published\": \"December 17, 2024\",\n      \"siteName\": \"www.fox5dc.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"8d8a723df1d33da4\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nElon Musk declares hashtags are dead: What it means for social media - PUSH.fm\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"8d8a723df1d33da4\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://blog.push.fm/19798/elon-musk-hashtags-dead/\",\n      \"description\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"7758c0dbd3a95d67\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nDeclining user engagement with hashtags – Studies have shown that engagement rates for hashtag-heavy posts are often lower than those without them, suggesting that audiences are less inclined to interact with such content. X’s evolving features – Since Musk’s takeover of X, the platform has focused on AI-driven content recommendations rather than relying on hashtags for content discovery.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"7758c0dbd3a95d67\\\">>>\",\n      \"published\": \"January 30, 2025\",\n      \"siteName\": \"blog.push.fm\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"23629ced13dfdc47\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nElon Musk declares hashtags obsolete - Netizency\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"23629ced13dfdc47\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://netizency.com/elon-musk-declares-hashtags-obsolete/\",\n      \"description\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"4c2ba55e9644a4e6\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nX’s AI has evolved beyond needing these manual markers. This isn’t just another Musk tweet – it’s a glimpse into social media’s AI-driven future. X’s algorithm can now read and understand your posts like a human would, making those carefully crafted hashtags as outdated as dial-up internet.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"4c2ba55e9644a4e6\\\">>>\",\n      \"published\": \"December 27, 2024\",\n      \"siteName\": \"netizency.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"7d46c0bc7913814c\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nX Bans Hashtags in Promoted Posts | Social Media Today\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"7d46c0bc7913814c\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.socialmediatoday.com/news/x-formerly-twitter-bans-hashtags-from-promoted-posts-ads/751782/\",\n      \"description\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"0a0903b0dd21375f\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nElon doesn&#x27;t like hashtags in ads, so <strong>X is banning them entirely</strong>.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"0a0903b0dd21375f\\\">>>\",\n      \"published\": \"June 26, 2025\",\n      \"siteName\": \"www.socialmediatoday.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"8e10403e03cebe59\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nElon Musk on X: \\\"Please stop using hashtags. The system doesn’t need them anymore and they look ugly.\\\" / X\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"8e10403e03cebe59\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://x.com/elonmusk/status/1869070358210572306?lang=en\",\n      \"description\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"f0fd15f6ad9de446\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nPlease stop using hashtags.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"f0fd15f6ad9de446\\\">>>\",\n      \"siteName\": \"x.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"3eef9503818569dd\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nr/EnoughMuskSpam on Reddit: Elon Musk announces major changes to X\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"3eef9503818569dd\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.reddit.com/r/EnoughMuskSpam/comments/1ll0rdm/elon_musk_announces_major_changes_to_x/\",\n      \"description\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"efc9f30264ca952e\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nMusk wrote on Thursday morning: &quot;Starting tomorrow, the esthetic nightmare that is hashtags will be banned from ads on X.&quot; OMG. What would the world do without Elons heroic work?\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"efc9f30264ca952e\\\">>>\",\n      \"published\": \"June 26, 2025\",\n      \"siteName\": \"www.reddit.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"9702bda1750a171a\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nElon Musk Tells X Users 'No Hashtags' And Guess What Happened Next\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"9702bda1750a171a\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://finance.yahoo.com/news/elon-musk-tells-x-users-004549756.html\",\n      \"description\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"85b9893d54091d06\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nElon Musk may own X, formerly Twitter, but that didn’t stop many of the social media platform’s users from giving him the business on Tuesday. What did the Tesla mogul do to deserve the snark? Well, he told the site’s users to no longer use hashtags to identify and organize specific topics.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"85b9893d54091d06\\\">>>\",\n      \"published\": \"December 19, 2024\",\n      \"siteName\": \"finance.yahoo.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"deff69ddd34d362b\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nElon Musk Announces Big Change Coming to X - Men's Journal\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"deff69ddd34d362b\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.mensjournal.com/news/elon-musk-announces-big-change-coming-x\",\n      \"description\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"eb2720687d53d7b9\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nElon Musk has made plenty of changes ... appreciate. Musk took to X on Thursday morning to announce that <strong>hashtags will no longer be allowed on ads on the platform</strong>....\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"eb2720687d53d7b9\\\">>>\",\n      \"published\": \"June 26, 2025\",\n      \"siteName\": \"www.mensjournal.com\"\n    }\n  ]\n}"}],"details":{"query":"Elon Musk hashtags dead Twitter 2026 what replaces hashtags","provider":"brave","count":8,"tookMs":3600,"externalContent":{"untrusted":true,"source":"web_search","provider":"brave","wrapped":true},"results":[{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"04f16085a94a9cfc\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nAre hashtags dead? Elon Musk says 'please stop' using them on X | FOX 5 DC\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"04f16085a94a9cfc\">>>","url":"https://www.fox5dc.com/news/hashtags-x-elon-musk-