se manual markers. This isn’t just another Musk tweet – it’s a glimpse into social media’s AI-driven future. X’s algorithm can now read and understand your posts like a human would, making those carefully crafted hashtags as outdated as dial-up internet.\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"4c2ba55e9644a4e6\">>>","published":"December 27, 2024","siteName":"netizency.com"},{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"7d46c0bc7913814c\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nX Bans Hashtags in Promoted Posts | Social Media Today\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"7d46c0bc7913814c\">>>","url":"https://www.socialmediatoday.com/news/x-formerly-twitter-bans-hashtags-from-promoted-posts-ads/751782/","description":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"0a0903b0dd21375f\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nElon doesn&#x27;t like hashtags in ads, so <strong>X is banning them entirely</strong>.\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"0a0903b0dd21375f\">>>","published":"June 26, 2025","siteName":"www.socialmediatoday.com"},{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"8e10403e03cebe59\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nElon Musk on X: \"Please stop using hashtags. The system doesn’t need them anymore and they look ugly.\" / X\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"8e10403e03cebe59\">>>","url":"https://x.com/elonmusk/status/1869070358210572306?lang=en","description":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"f0fd15f6ad9de446\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nPlease stop using hashtags.\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"f0fd15f6ad9de446\">>>","siteName":"x.com"},{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"3eef9503818569dd\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nr/EnoughMuskSpam on Reddit: Elon Musk announces major changes to X\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"3eef9503818569dd\">>>","url":"https://www.reddit.com/r/EnoughMuskSpam/comments/1ll0rdm/elon_musk_announces_major_changes_to_x/","description":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"efc9f30264ca952e\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nMusk wrote on Thursday morning: &quot;Starting tomorrow, the esthetic nightmare that is hashtags will be banned from ads on X.&quot; OMG. What would the world do without Elons heroic work?\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"efc9f30264ca952e\">>>","published":"June 26, 2025","siteName":"www.reddit.com"},{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"9702bda1750a171a\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nElon Musk Tells X Users 'No Hashtags' And Guess What Happened Next\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"9702bda1750a171a\">>>","url":"https://finance.yahoo.com/news/elon-musk-tells-x-users-004549756.html","description":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"85b9893d54091d06\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nElon Musk may own X, formerly Twitter, but that didn’t stop many of the social media platform’s users from giving him the business on Tuesday. What did the Tesla mogul do to deserve the snark? Well, he told the site’s users to no longer use hashtags to identify and organize specific topics.\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"85b9893d54091d06\">>>","published":"December 19, 2024","siteName":"finance.yahoo.com"},{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"deff69ddd34d362b\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nElon Musk Announces Big Change Coming to X - Men's Journal\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"deff69ddd34d362b\">>>","url":"https://www.mensjournal.com/news/elon-musk-announces-big-change-coming-x","description":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"eb2720687d53d7b9\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nElon Musk has made plenty of changes ... appreciate. Musk took to X on Thursday morning to announce that <strong>hashtags will no longer be allowed on ads on the platform</strong>....\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"eb2720687d53d7b9\">>>","published":"June 26, 2025","siteName":"www.mensjournal.com"}]},"isError":false,"timestamp":1777694319833}}
{"type":"message","id":"911a8705","parentId":"08a7afd8","timestamp":"2026-05-02T03:58:41.326Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now let me do a quick search specifically for Twitter/X engagement strategies for growing followers in 2026, and what's working specifically for the music + AI niche.","thinkingSignature":"6cbc03621cc120e8f50cacb76942aa263633f8e968e889484717b084f0e13150"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_wya2l0qxpg0l_1","name":"web_search","arguments":{"count":8,"query":"Twitter X engagement strategies grow followers 2026 viral posts algorithm tips"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":2127,"output":80,"cacheRead":88000,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":90207,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777694319840,"responseId":"0644a970976bcc53e65e9b725f0ec227"}}
{"type":"message","id":"dfd1f818","parentId":"911a8705","timestamp":"2026-05-02T03:58:43.474Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_wya2l0qxpg0l_1","toolName":"web_search","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"query\": \"Twitter X engagement strategies grow followers 2026 viral posts algorithm tips\",\n  \"provider\": \"brave\",\n  \"count\": 8,\n  \"tookMs\": 763,\n  \"externalContent\": {\n    \"untrusted\": true,\n    \"source\": \"web_search\",\n    \"provider\": \"brave\",\n    \"wrapped\": true\n  },\n  \"results\": [\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"c462436e8bd79b90\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nHow the Twitter Algorithm Works in 2026 [+6 Strategies] | Sprout Social\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"c462436e8bd79b90\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://sproutsocial.com/insights/twitter-algorithm/\",\n      \"description\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"4c80b29a197aa55e\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\n<strong>Structure your content to be shareable rather than just likeable</strong>. Ask yourself: “Is this useful enough to save for later?” (driving bookmarks) or “Is this important enough to share with others?” (driving reposts).\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"4c80b29a197aa55e\\\">>>\",\n      \"published\": \"March 31, 2026\",\n      \"siteName\": \"sproutsocial.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"89ba6212e32ea618\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nHow to Grow on Twitter/X: Complete Growth Strategy Guide 2026\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"89ba6212e32ea618\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://socialrails.com/blog/how-to-grow-on-twitter-x-complete-guide\",\n      \"description\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"90bac810a79511b5\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\n<strong>Use 1-2 relevant hashtags maximum</strong>. Twitter&#x27;s algorithm doesn&#x27;t favor heavy hashtag use like Instagram. Threads are crucial - they get 3x more engagement than single tweets and show expertise. No, follow accounts that provide value to you.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"90bac810a79511b5\\\">>>\",\n      \"published\": \"4 days ago\",\n      \"siteName\": \"socialrails.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"624cb92a9ea10cef\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nUnderstanding how the X (Twitter) algorithm works in 2026 - SocialBee\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"624cb92a9ea10cef\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://socialbee.com/blog/twitter-algorithm/\",\n      \"description\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"46c5e72fbee90bf9\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nInstead of manually testing dozens of time slots, you can use these recommendations to schedule tweets when your followers are most likely to see and interact with them. Over time, this helps your posts gather stronger early engagement signals, which increases the chances that the Twitter algorithm continues distributing them to more users. Smart marketers know the algorithm is constantly evolving, so having SocialBee’s informed recommendations can make your work much easier. ... On X, visibility often grows through conversations.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"46c5e72fbee90bf9\\\">>>\",\n      \"published\": \"4 days ago\",\n      \"siteName\": \"socialbee.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"561dd8d57317ea71\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nHow to Grow Your X (Formerly Twitter) Following in 2026\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"561dd8d57317ea71\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://kickofflabs.com/blog/top-tips-growing-twitter-following/\",\n      \"description\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"b2d83821e0be4440\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nTo grow a following on X in 2026, brands need to <strong>optimize their profiles, post consistently with long-form and video content, engage authentically in Communities and Spaces, and consider X Premium for algorithmic visibility</strong>.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"b2d83821e0be4440\\\">>>\",\n      \"published\": \"March 15, 2026\",\n      \"siteName\": \"kickofflabs.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"f860df0715929cdf\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\n10 Effective Strategies on How to Increase the Followers on Twitter\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"f860df0715929cdf\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://tweetfull.com/blog/how-to-increase-the-followers-on-twitter-in-2026-without-fake-growth/\",\n      \"description\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"d3240d7d415de565\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nThe 2025–2026 algorithm favors <strong>watch time, meaningful replies, and consistent activity over one-off viral hits</strong>. Accounts that post 1-3 high-quality tweets daily alongside regular engagement see 10%+ monthly follower growth, compared to the ...\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"d3240d7d415de565\\\">>>\",\n      \"published\": \"January 22, 2026\",\n      \"siteName\": \"tweetfull.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"68c932639f73550f\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nUnlocking X (Formally Twitter) Success in 2026: Innovative Growth Hacks and Strategies You Need to Try\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"68c932639f73550f\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.socialmediacowboys.com/post/unlocking-twitter-success-in-2026-innovative-growth-hacks-and-strategies-you-need-to-try\",\n      \"description\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"edf8f77f5ed9975c\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nX (Twitter) continues to evolve rapidly, and 2026 brings fresh opportunities for users to grow their presence and boost engagement. The platform’s algorithm updates, new tools, and shifting user behaviors require a new approach to stand out. 